org.dmd.dmc.presentation
Class Tracker

java.lang.Object
  org.dmd.dmc.presentation.Tracker
All Implemented Interfaces:
DmcPresentationTrackerIF
public class Tracker
extends java.lang.Object
implements DmcPresentationTrackerIF

The Tracker implements the DmcPresentationTrackerIF interface and can be used to track the readiness and change status of one or more generated form bindings (that result from FormBindingDefinitions in Model View Whatever).

Simply set a tracker on your generated form bindings and then use components similar to the GxtCancel or GxtApply buttons (org.dmd.mvw.client.gxtforms.implementation) to allow users to submit changes or cancel any changes they've made.
